    <PrimAttribute name="number" id="98cda22e-791b-4e6e-85c4-38933fac02fa">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Integer"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>
This number is used for the Translations.  The myRoot inverse
is used to ensure uniqueness.  This is set to the objects 
instanceID as a way to generate a unique number within the
DEV environment.  This number is then stored in the XML which
is shipped out to clients. 

In this way the number should be the same at all client sites.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
